com.sensorstack

Class ContinuousStreamInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sensorstack.ContinuousStreamInfo

  • public class ContinuousStreamInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    ContinuousStreamInfo represents the parameters needed to fetch, unpack and validate continuous streaming data. All data members have been initialised.
